details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: We've got an upper hand in this fight now.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: Our base is nearly done, Sir. A couple of buildings still need crew.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: What is the situation at the river crossing?

details.name: Infantry
details.text: Take a look at this intel, Sir.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: The bridge is heavily guarded by armour and infantry.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: It is supplied by a small checkpoint nearby.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: The other side is guarded as well.

details.name: Infantry
details.text: A much larger instalation is present there as well.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: That HQ building must be coordinating all of their forces. Taking it is our main objective.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Where is our air support?

details.name: Infantry
details.text: On it's way, should be here very soon.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Good. Start building up our army in the meantime, then attack that checkpoint.

details.name: Attack Helicopter
details.text: Air support is in the area. Waiting for orders.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: A veteran Attack Helicopter will be very useful.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Our tower has been monitoring this flank.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: It appears there are no enemy units on this side. The way to the enemy HQ is wide open.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: The only problem is the river. It is very wide and deep. This is where that helicopter comes in.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: An Attack Helicopter is capable of carrying a single Infantry unit on board. If we can ferry a few units, we can perform a back attack.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Make sure that they have cover, as these Infantry units will not be able to do anything until their next turn, right after deployment.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: We can also use our helicopters to perform flanking attacks on enemy units trying to hold or cross the bridge. Any Tank will be a sitting duck.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Without their command center, enemy forces will disperse. Let's secure this base and start bringing our Tanks over the bridge for the final assault.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: No! How could I fail?
